Subject: Re: Fractals? what good are they?
Message-ID: <C52wBw.CGI@mentor.cc.purdue.edu>
Sender: news@mentor.cc.purdue.edu (USENET News)
Organization: Purdue University
References: <7155@pdxgate.UUCP>
